<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka lawite! en tiem u hetna,
 Van a khun a um;
 Ei panpih ding a lang ta ie,
 Zawhna ding a nai.

[V2]
 &quot;Na pang un la hung ding ka hi&quot;
 Lal Isu'n A tii;
 Van lamah dawnna pieu un la,
 &quot;Nang ziek' Pang kau&quot; tiin.

[V3]
 2. En tiem u, dogal a hung ui,
 Setan puih huoi in;
 I velah mi hangsan puk ui,
 I zolo vang ui!

[V4]
 3. En un puonlap lopi aphei!
 Pengkun gi ngaiun!
 I puipau min in zo hitiu,
 Dogal tincheng chuh.

[V5]
 4. Gal lauhum sawtpi do mahleng,
 Panpih ding anai;
 Pangun, I Puipau A hung hi,
 Lawite, kipak un.</lyrics>
<title>HOLD THE FORT</title>
<hymn_number>315</hymn_number>
</song>